OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FUK's first drug consumption
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Froom given go-ahead        
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The UK's first official consumption    
OL,6, room for illegal drugs including heroin
OL,7, and cocaine has been approved by       
OL,8, authorities in Glasgow.                
OL,10,FThe facility is backed by the Scottish 
OL,11,Fgovernment as a way to tackle the      
OL,12,Fcountry's drugs deaths crisis.         
OL,14,FThe pilot scheme will be based at a    
OL,15,Fhealth centre in the east end of       
OL,16,FGlasgow.                               
OL,18,FIt will see users take their own drugs 
OL,19,Funder the supervision of trained health
OL,20,Fprofessionals.                         
